The hotel was lovely, our room was quite exceptional with a bathroom and a shower room and beautifully furnished and spotless [room number one].	The standard room is small, but the bathroom was a decent size, which is often not the case with European design hotels.	The room was akin to a junior suite, with an anteroom for the sofa bed, a B/O television and high ceilings.	Our room was very large-(I believe it was a junior suite) with the bathroom on the first level along with a sitting area and bedroom upstairs.